==BETHELE==
Bethele ke motsana o o fitlhelwang kwa barolong le tshimo tsa barolong, o itsege ka Morolong. O supelwa ntlheng tsa tsela ya LObatse Ramatlabama, o dikhilometara dile tlhano gotswa motseng wa pitsane. Ntleng le ditshingwana tsa barolong, baga Montshioa Bethele o ageletse barolong, bahurutshi le batlhaping. Rrampudi waga Mopedi eleng ene wa ntlha go dula mo lefelong le, one ele Lehurutshi-moshaneng ka ntlha ya aparateiti.
